      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KEAYANG SWEETHEART (2) made it two from two with a resuming win at Geelong then drew on the back row and finished third at her latest appearance at Terang. Progressive and gets a nice draw on the front line. That could see her back in the winners' list. WICKED CONFESSION (8) made it three in a row by winning the rich Running of the Bulls last start. Tougher draw but came from this row to win easily prior so could continue on her winning way  OZZIE PEARL (1) has been a model of consistency of late and deserved her success last start, coming from much wider and scoring by 1.5 metres at Swan Hill. Should enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position so is worth including along with THE GOLDEN HOOK (7) who has come from the back line to salute in his last two outings here.",
